title: [Guardian Keep, Market Office]
description: The towering inner keep wall occupies the northern part of this grassy sward.  Constructed right up against the north wall is a large stone building.  A wooden sign overhanging the building entrance clearly states the establishment's purpose.

The towering inner keep wall occupies the northern part of this grassy sward.  The shape of a large building can be barely seen constructed right up against the north wall.  Light from a nearby window reveals a wooden sign overhanging the building entrance, which clearly states the establishment's purpose.
